{"tid":515668,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)舊版蝙蝠俠1-4","createTime":"2017-12-31T15:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T22:24:35.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b380ce868c6728f2943490945fad307fc9a21236","tid":515668,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=k5mLwpxTW8N2%2Bo39%2FSNUUFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=967ece1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=k5mLwpxTW8N2%2Bo39%2FSNUUFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=00418386\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3c/Batman_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3c%2FBatman_ver2.jpg&h=ef8dd305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.紐約市的百萬富翁布魯斯&middot;韋恩掌管著韋恩家族企業。童年，父母和他有一次從劇院走出來時遇到搶劫，父母雙雙被歹徒打死，布魯斯因此成為孤兒。成年後的布魯斯開始向犯罪復仇，他化作披著斗篷，戴著面具的蝙蝠俠。以韋恩企業的經濟實力為後盾，用高科技武器裝備自己，在黑夜出動打擊犯罪活動。蝙蝠俠的行動引起了媒體的注意，記者斯諾對其的報導引起了女攝影師維琪的注意，她主動與斯諾合作開始調查蝙蝠俠的真實身份。他們打算在即將舉行的布魯斯&middot;韋恩的慈善晚會上向警察局長高登提出問題。布魯斯在晚會上遇到維琪，對其產生好感<br />\n<br />\n2.一對夫妻生下了一個貌似企鵝的畸形兒奧斯瓦爾德（Oswald），他們不喜歡奧斯瓦爾德而把他鎖在籠子丟棄到了河裡。順著河流企鵝來到了下水道。鏡頭轉到30年後，史勒克和市長一起和市民慶祝聖誕節。事後史勒克向市長提議城市繼續建發電廠，藉此他的私人工廠可以汲取城市電能。市長否決了他的提案。於是他和奧斯瓦爾德合謀讓小丑劫持市長兒子，然後由奧斯瓦爾德拯救，繼而成為城市的英雄代替原市長..<br />\n<br />\n3.在高譚城，蝙蝠俠阻止了由雙面人引起的一起銀行人質事件，但雙面人還是逃脫了，他以前曾是地區檢察官哈維&middot;登特，因為遭受了巨大的不幸而變成一個邪惡的魔頭。愛德華&middot;奈格瑪是韋恩企業的一名研究人員，他開發出一種可以直接和人腦相連接的機器，通曉他人思想並加以控制的機器。布魯斯&middot;韋恩認為這樣的發明會引起太多的爭議，因此拒絕採納。愛德華於是憤怒地殺死了自己的上司並偽造成自殺後辭職<br />\n<br />\n4.神出鬼沒的蝙蝠俠，這回將面臨此生中最強勁的對手&mdash;急凍人、毒藤女和他的跟班&mdash;班恩。勇敢機敏的蝙蝠女孩與蝙蝠俠和羅賓聯手，同與邪惡的罪犯展開了對戰..<br />\n<br />\n12 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=k5mLwpxTW8N2%2Bo39%2FSNUUFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=73af8313\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=k5mLwpxTW8N2%2Bo39%2FSNUUFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=c596f9ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a829a0c97441cdca8ef5d657c1a06cc0397a16","tid":515668,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d602dd5f79e1db2ad502c9d43b67ea4aaac25c49","tid":515668,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T16:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a071113b4db564c106c5e3e5115d56be36e30688","tid":515668,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 